From: Tom Huynh <tom.huynh@freescale.com>
Date: Fri, 17 Apr 2015 14:03:40 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 011/214] fsl/ls2085a: add entry for ccn-504

Add dts entry for ccn-504 to work with ccn-504 perf driver

References:
- upstream commit a33b0daab73a ("bus: ARM CCN PMU driver")
- LS2085A RM:
	Table 2-1. CCSR Block Base Address Map
	Section 5-2 Internal Interrupt Sources

Signed-off-by: Tom Huynh <tom.huynh@freescale.com>
Change-Id: I41fca05b7a253a503f1358ecec345fea57bfcc91
Reviewed-on: http://git.am.freescale.net:8181/35234
Tested-by: Review Code-CDREVIEW <CDREVIEW@freescale.com>
Reviewed-by: Bhupesh Sharma <bhupesh.sharma@freescale.com>
Reviewed-by: Stuart Yoder <stuart.yoder@freescale.com>
[Original patch extracted from FSL LS2085 SDK EAR5.0,
Layerscape2-SDK-SOURCE-20150828-yocto.iso]
Signed-off-by: Jiang Lu <lu.jiang@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-ls2085a.dtsi | 6 ++++++
 1 file changed, 6 insertions(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-ls2085a.dtsi b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-ls2085a.dtsi
index 21aa411..5d0bccd 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-ls2085a.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-ls2085a.dtsi
@@ -598,6 +598,12 @@
 		lpi-parent = <&its>;
 	};
 
+	ccn@4000000 {
+		compatible = "arm,ccn-504";
+		reg = <0x0 0x04000000 0x0 0x01000000>;
+		interrupts = <0 12 4>;
+	};
+
 	memory@80000000 {
 		device_type = "memory";
 		reg = <0x00000000 0x80000000 0 0x80000000>;
